{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5a68c5ce76","title":"关于全牙拉本兵团及七溪守敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c4496d8566","index":0,"year":1950,"month":10,"day":11,"articleId":"5a68c5ce76"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"61f76016d3","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"5a68c5ce76","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会起草的给中国人民解放军西南军区副司令员、云南军区司令员陈康的电报。陈当时率派越南，以中共中央代表身份协助越共中央和越南人民军总部组织指挥抗击法国侵略军的边界战役。"},{"id":"e8e1d8795d","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"5a68c5ce76","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"拉本，当时任驻越南七溪地区的法国军队指挥官。越南边界战役期间，曾奉命率由外籍部队组成的4个连增援部队，北上解救在谷社山区被越南人民军包围的法军。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f40cd57f6b","type":"title","text":"关于全齐拉本兵团及七溪守敌！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"5a68c5ce76"},{"id":"61f76016d3","type":"paragraph","text":"陈质：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"5a68c5ce76"},{"id":"e8e1d8795d","type":"paragraph","text":"九日电悉。为了争取边界战役的完满胜利，必须鼓励士气，全纤拉本兵团及七溪守敌。当攻七溪时，谅山等处法军还是可能增援的，此点应预先估计到并作阻援或打援部署","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"5a68c5ce76"},{"id":"65cecf8d3d","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"5a68c5ce76"},{"id":"0116664f09","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"5a68c5ce76"}],"page":{"id":"8344f3c0d4","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"5a68c5ce76","start":228,"end":228}}}},"__N_SSG":true}